<div style="font-family: 'Arial', sans-serif; max-width: 600px; margin: auto; padding: 20px; background-color: #ffffff; border: 1px solid #e0e0e0; border-radius: 8px; box-shadow: 0 4px 20px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);">
  <h2 style="color: #333; text-align: center; font-size: 26px; margin-bottom: 20px; font-weight: bold;">Password Reset Instructions</h2>
  
  <p style="color: #555; line-height: 1.6; font-size: 16px;">
    Hi <%= @resource.email %>!
  </p>
  
  <p style="color: #555; line-height: 1.6; font-size: 16px;">
    We received a request to reset your password. You can reset your password by clicking the button below:
  </p>

  <p style="text-align: center;">
    <a href="http://localhost:3000/reset-password?reset_password_token=<%= @reset_password_token %>" 
       style="display: inline-block; padding: 15px 30px; margin: 20px 0; 
              background: linear-gradient(to right, #6a11cb, #2575fc); color: white; 
              text-align: center; text-decoration: none; border-radius: 5px; 
              font-size: 18px; font-weight: bold; transition: background-color 0.3s, transform 0.2s;">
      Reset Password
    </a>
  </p>

  <p style="text-align: center; color: #555; font-size: 14px; margin-top: -10px;">Click the button above to proceed.</p>

  <hr style="border: 0; border-top: 1px solid #e0e0e0; margin: 20px 0;">

  <p style="color: #555; line-height: 1.6; font-size: 16px;">
    If you didn't request a password reset, please ignore this email. Your account will remain secure, and your password wonâ€™t change until you access the link above and create a new one.
  </p>

  <p style="color: #777; text-align: center; margin-top: 30px; font-size: 14px;">
    Thank you,<br>
    The Support Team
  </p>
  
  <footer style="margin-top: 20px; text-align: center; font-size: 12px; color: #aaa; line-height: 1.4;">
    <p style="margin: 0;">This email was sent to you because we received a request to reset your password.</p>
    <p style="margin: 0;">If you believe this was a mistake, please contact our support team at <a href="mailto:support@example.com" style="color: #2575fc; text-decoration: none;">support@example.com</a>.</p>
  </footer>
</div>


